MISCELLANEOUS DISMISSALS

2002-1542. State ex rel. Ramirez-Garcia v. Pagan.

In Mandamus. This cause originated in this court on the filing of a complaint for a writ of mandamus. Upon consideration of relator’s response to the show-cause order issued by this court on November 25, 2002,

IT IS ORDERED by the court, sua sponte, that this cause be, and hereby is, dismissed.
